\f0\fs24 \cf0 Lauren Lotka is a successful entrepreneur, business development and talent consultant who partners with designers and brands to help them access exceptional talent and streamline business initiatives to execute better ideas faster.\
\
With experience in brand strategy, business development, licensing + joint ventures, marketing, brand partnerships and collaborations, investment prospects, senior talent and executive search, Lauren has spent the past 15 years facilitating the ins and outs of building and growing successful brands globally.
\b  
\b0 Whether her clients need strategy, a catalyst, an expert, or an idea to get to the next phase of growth, she connects the big ideas with the right talent to incite and impact change.
\b \

